<title>Help Us Out  &middot; #smarnold</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="help-us-out/style.css">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

<body>
  <div class="help-page">

    <div class="hero">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Help Us Out</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="intro">
      <p>A bunch of people have asked how they can contribute to our wedding plans. In all seriousness, the best contribution you can make is to be there on the day. But if you'd like to help us out a little more, here are a few other ideas!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-section">
      <div class="help-section-content">
        <h2>Buy a bit of our honeymoon</h2>

        <p>We're going to Japan for our honeymoon. There's lots of things we'd like to do while we're there, and it would be really lovely if you could buy a bit of our itinerary.</p>

        <p>You can check out our plans and contribute <a href="/holiday-wishlist">here</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="help-section-image-container">
        <img class="help-section-image" src="/help-us-out/wave.png" />
        <div class="help-section-caption">切手を二枚をください。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-section help-section-left-image">
      <div class="help-section-content">
        <h2>Get crafty</h2>

        <p>It's going to be a big ol' marquee, so we'll need a bunch of nice things to fill it. In particular, we'd appreciate it if you'd like to make some bunting for us to hang up around the marquee.</p>

        <p>For more information on what we're looking for, head <a href="/bunting">here</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="help-section-image-container">
        <img class="help-section-image" src="/help-us-out/art.png" />
        <div class="help-section-caption">Ooo, crafty.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-section">
      <div class="help-section-content">
        <h2>Bake</h2>

        <p>We're not going to have a wedding cake, but you might be aware we are quite into dessert. If you'd like to show off your baking skills (and you're confident you can get your creation to North Hill Farm in one piece!), we'd love it if you'd bring something for the dessert table.</p>

        <p>If you are planning to bring something along, let us know when you <a href="/rsvp">RSVP</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="help-section-image-container">
        <img class="help-section-image" src="/help-us-out/gbbo.png" />
        <div class="help-section-caption">Ready, set, bake!</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
